Sample Readme

# Project Title
PDF and Image Metadata extractor

# Prerequisite
Python 2.7
Terminal
Ubuntu

# Brief Description
Python scripts to extract metadata from a pdf file and an image file.
Usage 
cd to project folder
    
Running image.py
python image.py -f "path_to_the_image_file"
eg python image.py -f /home/ulrich/Desktop/imageTest/ulrich.jpg

Running pdf.py
python pdf.py -f "path_to_a_pdf_file"
eg python pdf.py -f /home/ulrich/Desktop/Python/security.pdf

# Conclusion

